data.text:
2018-19: Did not see any game action.

COMMUNITY COLLEGE: Played the 2017 season at Butler CC under head coach Tim Schaffner... Started at right tackle, helping the Grizzlies earn an 8-3 record and average 182.8 rushing yards per game… Redshirted the 2016 season… Played with current Wildcats Chris Dugan, Noah Johnson, Jahron McPherson and Ty Zentner.

HIGH SCHOOL: A two-year letterwinner at Hayden under head coach Bill Arnold.

PERSONAL: Justin David Eichman was born November 24, 1997, in Topeka, Kansas... Son of David and Teresa Eichman... Mother attended K-State... Has one sister, Cristina... Majoring in management.
